WEBVTT

00:00:00.152 --> 00:00:09.099
We operate in a boundaryless organizational environment where technological acceleration, cultural friction, and human sustainability constantly converge.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.122
The traditional rulebooks of management have been rendered obsolete.

00:00:13.983 --> 00:00:19.908
We demand strict practical relevance to your career and the complex social systems you navigate daily.

00:00:20.777 --> 00:00:23.304
You are here to develop a performance of understanding.

00:00:24.106 --> 00:00:32.168
You have not truly learned these concepts until you can actively apply, analyze, and create new knowledge to solve the undefined challenges

00:00:32.248 --> 00:00:32.830
waiting for you.
